Module count
Package count.model

Class RELL

java.lang.Object
count.model.RELL
public class RELL
extends Object
Joint evaluation of a set of rate models by bootstrapping. Add models one by one using addRates(TreeWithRates), then call getBootstrapWinners(Random, int) and getBootstrapSupport(int[], TreeComparator) to translate into edge support for a chosen phylogeny.

    • getBootstrapSupport

      public int[] getBootstrapSupport​(int[] winners, TreeComparator cmp)
      Translates winning statistics into bootstrap edge support for first model, for the unrooted phylogeny.
      Parameters:
      winners - array of bootstrap winning statistics from getBootstrapWinners(Random, int)
      cmp - the reference tree whose edges are to be annotated (use one of the tested models)
      Returns:
      bootstrap support: how many times each edge was present in bootstrap winners
